attributionInfo.brokerName: Coldwell Banker Sea Coast Advantage - Jacksonville
THE REAL ESTATE CENTER OF NEW BERN, INC

data.description: This beautiful Forest Run home offers all of the upgrades including high baseboards and crown molding throughout, granite countertops, detailed ceilings and a huge fenced-in backyard. Welcome guests from the rocking chair front porch into the open concept, split bedroom floor plan. Notice a formal dining room with coffered ceiling perfect for the upcoming holidays. Hardwood flooring leads you to gather for conversations around a cozy gas log fireplace under a tray ceiling in the living room. Easily entertain while preparing meals in the kitchen finished with a decorative tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a pantry for added storage and a breakfast nook for quick meals. Off the kitchen and living room is access to the screened porch, spacious deck and fenced-in backyard where you can enjoy hosting cookouts and yard games or simply relaxing with a beverage and good read in the sunshine. Retreat to the first floor primary bedroom with a tray ceiling where relaxation comes naturally after a busy day. Pass dual closets before entering the en suite bathroom complete with a dual sink vanity, jetted tub and a walk-in shower. Two spare bedrooms on the first floor offer guests a comfortable space of their own. Head upstairs where you have a fourth bedroom or bonus room offering a private bathroom with a walk-in shower. Bountiful attic storage, a laundry room with cabinets and counter space, and an attached two car garage with added storage and a utility sink complete this amazing property. Located in an award winning school district with NO city taxes, find yourself just minutes from everything New Bern has to offer including the Historic Downtown while a quick car ride takes you to MCAS Cherry Point in Havelock or North Carolina's Crystal Coast beaches. Contact us today for your private tour of this stunning property!
